<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-tag">Questions</div>
      <h2>Things people ask before they buy</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do I need to know how to code to use your templates?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Not at all. Every template comes with a clear setup guide and clearly labeled placeholder text throughout the code. If you can use Microsoft Word, you can set up my templates.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What do I need to go live with a template?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">A domain name (about $12/year from Namecheap or Google Domains) and free hosting on Netlify. The setup guide walks you through both. Or choose Done-For-You and I handle everything.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How is this different from Wix, Squarespace, or WordPress?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Those platforms charge $16&ndash;$45/month forever. My templates are yours to own. Pay once, host free on Netlify, never pay again. Plus they&rsquo;re hand-coded to be fast and clean &mdash; no bloat.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How long does a Done-For-You setup take?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Typically 3&ndash;5 business days from when I receive your content (logo, photos, text, colors). I&rsquo;ll send you a simple form to fill out &mdash; no coding or special formats required.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I see an example of your full custom work?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes &mdash; visit <a href="https://www.enduringbranches.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--navy);font-weight:700">enduringbranches.com</a>. Blog, store, prayer request system, email notifications, full admin dashboard &mdash; all built from scratch.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What if I need an industry that&rsquo;s not in your template shop?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Just reach out and request it. I build on demand &mdash; you pay for the custom build, and I add it to the shop so others can benefit too.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

